PrecisAppointment of Kelly Gibney, of Burnaby, British Columbia, as a governor of the Council of the Canadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety, being the nominee of the Business Council of British Columbia, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of William Mathieson, who has resigned.
